        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 8:29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Some think it was symbolic of the stoning which was the penalty of a rebel son (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 21:20-21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
